{"tid":623174,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插沙] 點樣可以喺英國補辦特區護照?","createTime":"2018-04-09T18:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T18:40:43.000Z","uid":27570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7dacc5e8b3d4257a919243975b5f5048267bd210","tid":623174,"uid":27570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T18:19:01.000Z","msg":"小弟而家喺英國讀書<br />\n但幾日前去歐洲旅行，但喺荷蘭俾賊仔偷左本passport <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾經波折，終於翻返去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問巴打點樣可以喺英國補翻本地區護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我7月中就翻香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   會唔會翻唔到黎嫁？"},{"pid":"6b497df7bea839f2fe021fe4f3e235580a37f378","tid":623174,"uid":27570,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T18:22:19.000Z","msg":"我而家有喺荷蘭嘅報案紙，同埋喺中国比利時大使館搞嘅臨時旅遊證。<br />\n<br />\n我呢個case 最好嘅方法要點做?"},{"pid":"3457e34e6ecb2f561c0278d6fcf5059701f8c427","tid":623174,"uid":27570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf356fb1ba481e9ba7e1816ac62f7a04b773518d","tid":623174,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T18:25:50.000Z","msg":"冇特區護照都返到香港"},{"pid":"eb5ed777b61c654c9c66f63f01eee2495f178a77","tid":623174,"uid":35846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T18:26:33.000Z","msg":"身分證呢"},{"pid":"e660bcbfc951076d424a1ae03e1d9e916b01cefd","tid":623174,"uid":80533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T18:27:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/service/travel_document/apply_for_hksar_passport.html#bb&amp;secondTab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservice%2Ftravel_document%2Fapply_for_hksar_passport.html%23bb%26secondTab&d=rt6lTYIo5Ld7Bxv0KkJlZAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=4f097b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/service/travel_document/apply_for_hksar_passport.html#bb&amp;secondTab</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>於 香 港 以 外 遞 交 申 請</strong></span><br />\n親 身 遞 交 或 郵 遞<br />\n申 請 人 應 透 過 最 就 近 的 中 國 駐 外 國 的 使 領 館 遞 交 申 請<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>申 請 書</strong></span><br />\n申 請 人 可 以 在 此 下 載 兩 類 海 外 申 請 書 及 說 明 書 ：<br />\n 用 於 16 歲 或 以 上 人 士 的 海 外 申 請 書 （ 表 格 ID 843 ）<br />\n如 申 請 人 原 有 的 香 港 特 別 行 政 區 護 照 已 遺 失 、 損 毁 、 殘 破 或 無 法 使 用 ， 須 額 外 填 寫 表 格 (ID645)<br />\n<br />\ngoogle都懶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2ca69c6f2da9c6596a540d1eb7af142d6ee116","tid":623174,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T18:28:40.000Z","msg":"要補領咪去大使館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinese-embassy.org.uk/chn/lsfw/hzlxz/blxz/t1267852.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinese-embassy.org.uk%2Fchn%2Flsfw%2Fhzlxz%2Fblxz%2Ft1267852.htm&d=rt6lTYIo5Ld7Bxv0KkJlZAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1bd16f94\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinese-embassy.org.uk/chn/lsfw/hzlxz/blxz/t1267852.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1458781d1fbcc778dc07d480bdeef5b93bc1e3ff","tid":623174,"uid":27605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T18:29:57.000Z","msg":"趕住返咪做個旅行證 比你返香港"},{"pid":"b58c096bf4743368aaf1364504fc41f1